re%20is%20a%20provision%20for%20investigation%20after%20the%20game%20if%20a%20timewasting%20is%20found%20to%20be%20deliberate.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20umpires%20believe%20that%20the%20act%20of%20time%20wasting%20was%20deliberate%20or%20repetitive%2C%20they%20may%20lodge%20a%20report%20under%20the%20ICC%20Code%20of%20Conduct.%20In%20such%20circumstances%20the%20Captain%20and%2For%20any%20individual%20members%20of%20the%20fielding%20team%20responsible%20for%20the%20time%20wasting%20will%20be%20charged%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20ICC%20playing%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20such%20news%20has%20come%20so%20far%20that%20the%20match%20officials%20and%20ICC%20are%20opening%20an%20investigation%20against%20Naib.%20Also%2C%20Naib%20has%20said%20that%20he%20was%20facing%20injury%20issues%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20time-wasting%20was%20deliberate.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719379500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fqp9gekt_naib_625x300_25_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fgulbadin-naib-faces-ban-for-faking-injury-in-afghanistans-t20-world-cup-thriller-icc-rule-says-this-5969757%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gulbadin%20Naib%2C%20who%20was%20fielding%20in%20the%20slip%20cordon%2C%20complained%20of%20cramps%20during%20the%2012th%20over%20bowled%20by%20spinner%20Noor%20Ahmad%2C%20after%20Trott%20was%20seen%20on%20camera%20asking%20his%20players%20to%20slow%20down%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fgulbadin-naib-faces-ban-for-faking-injury-in-afghanistans-t20-world-cup-thriller-icc-rule-says-this-5969757%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fgulbadin-naib-faces-ban-for-faking-injury-in-afghanistans-t20-world-cup-thriller-icc-rule-says-this-5969757%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%2