leh%20was%20found%20murdered%20in%20his%20%242.4%20million%207th-floor%20high-rise%20condo%20on%20East%20Houston%20Street%2C%20reported%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F06%2F24%2Fus-news%2Ftech-ceo-fahim-salehs-ex-assistant-convicted-in-grisly-dismemberment-murder%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3ENY%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EPlanning%20the%20murder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTyrese%20Haspil's%20scheme%20to%20steal%20from%20his%20former%20boss%2C%20Fahim%20Saleh%2C%20began%20in%202018%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20until%20July%202020%20that%20his%20plan%20turned%20deadly.%C2%A0He%20embezzled%20money%20from%20Mr%20Saleh's%20companies%20to%20purchase%20lavish%20gifts%20for%20his%20girlfriend%2C%20The%20NYT%20reported.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHaspil%20created%20a%20bogus%20corporate%20entity%20and%20bank%20account%20to%20funnel%20the%20stolen%20money.%20When%20Mr%20Saleh%20discovered%20the%20theft%20in%20January%202020%2C%20Haspil%20agreed%20to%20a%20repayment%20plan%20but%20continued%20to%20steal%20more%20money%20through%20a%20fraudulent%20PayPal%20account.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnConcerned%20that%20Mr%20Saleh%20would%20discover%20the%20more%20lucrative%20theft%2C%20Haspil%20began%20plotting%20to%20kill%20him.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTyrese%20Haspil's%20online%20activity%20showed%20that%20he%20searched%20for%20%26quot%3BFahim%20Saleh%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmurder%20of%20tech%20CEO%20in%20New%20York%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%26quot%3Bdismembered%20body%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Banatomy%20of%20the%20human%20neck%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20looked%20up%20building%20plans%20and%20searched%20for%20contractor-grade%20trash%20bags%2C%20weapons%20and%20cleaning%20supplies%2C%20as%20per%20the%20NYT.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHaspil%20also%20tracked%20Mr%20Saleh's%20whereabouts%20on%20social%20media%20and%20purchased%20clothes%20to%20conceal%20his%20identity.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EExecution%20of%20the%20murder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20July%2013%2C%202020%2C%20Tyrese%20Haspil%20entered%20an%20elevator%20with%20Mr%20Saleh%20in%20the%20latter's%20apartment%20building%20wearing%20a%20dark%20plastic%20face%20shield%2C%20a%20baseball%20cap%20and%20sunglasses.%20Mr%20Saleh%2C%20unaware%20of%20the%20impending%20danger%2C%20joked%20with%20Haspil%20about%20taking%20Covid%20precautions%20seriously.%20However%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20elevator%20doors%20opened%2C%20Haspil's%20demeanour%20turned%20deadly.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20his%20testimony%2C%20Tyrese%20Haspil%20tased%20Fahim%20Saleh%20in%20the%20back%2C%20rendering%20him%20immobile%2C%20and%20then%20pulled%20out%20a%20knife.%20With%20a%20targeted%20strike%2C%20Haspil%20aimed%20for%20Mr%20Saleh's%20neck%2C%20delivering%20a%20fatal%20blow%2C%20reported%20the%20NYT.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20then%20left%20the%20apartment%20and%20returned%20the%20next%20day%20to%20dismember%20Mr%20Saleh's%20body%20with%20an%20electric%20saw.%20He%20stuffed%20the%20body%20parts%20in%20plastic%20bags%2C%20which%20were%20later%20found%20strewn%20across%20the%20apartment.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHowever%2C%20before%20completing%20the%20task%2C%20he%20left%20again%20to%20purchase%20a%20battery%20charger%2C%20and%20it%20was%20during%20this%20time%20that%20Fahim%20Saleh's%20cousin%20discovered%20the%20scene%20when%20he%20went%20to%20check%20up%20on%20him.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTyrese%20Haspil%20was%20arrested%20four%20days%20later%20at%20an%20Airbnb%20he%20booked%20for%20his%20girlfriend's%20birthday%20celebration.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHis%20public%20defenders%20argued%20that%20he%20murdered%20his%20ex-boss%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cextreme%20emotional%20disturbance%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cunconditional%20love%E2%80%9D%20for%20his%20girlfriend.%20He%20feared%20she%20would%20leave%20him%20if%20she%20found%20out%20he%20had%20been%20embezzling%20money%20from%20his%20boss%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca