%20support%20of%20the%20four%20MPs%20of%20YS%20Jaganmohan%20Reddy's%20YSR%20Congress.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20stage%20was%20set%20for%20the%20election%20when%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Congress%20decided%20to%20field%20K%20Suresh%20just%2010%20minutes%20ahead%20of%20the%20noon%20deadline.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIts%20decision%20was%20spurred%20by%20the%20BJP%20brush-off%20to%20its%20hopes%20for%20the%20Pro%20Tem%20Speaker%20and%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker%20posts.%20The%20party%20had%20initially%20expected%20Mr%20Suresh%20-%20the%20senior%20most%20MP%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20-%20to%20get%20the%20post%20of%20Pro%20Tem%20Speaker%2C%20which%20finally%20went%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Bhartruhari%20Mahtab.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOn%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20the%20government%2C%20while%20seeking%20consensus%20for%20Om%20Birla%2C%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20they%20are%20not%20considering%20a%20Deputy%20Speaker%20post%2C%20or%20the%20Opposition's%20claim%20to%20it%2C%20for%20now.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECongress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRajnath%20Singh%20called%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20extend%20support...%20the%20entire%20Opposition%20said%20we%20will%20support%20but%20convention%20is%20Deputy%20Speaker%20should%20be%20from%20our%20side.%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20he%20would%20call%20back...%20but%20he%20has%20not%20yet...PM%20is%20asking%20for%20cooperation%20but%20our%20leader%20is%20getting%20insulted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EParallel%20meetings%20at%20both%20camps%20marked%20Tuesday%20evening.%20While%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20met%20the%20NDA%20allies%2C%20the%20Opposition%20Bloc%20had%20their%20meeting%20at%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20house.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20signalled%20that%20it%20did%20not%20approve%20the%20decision%20to%20force%20a%20contest.%20After%20publicly%20complaining%20that%20it%20was%20not%20consulted%2C%20the%20party%20came%20around