0at%20The%20Ritz%20Paris%20wearing%20a%20striking%20one-shoulder%20red%20minidress.%20However%2C%20as%20she%20ascended%20the%20steps%20of%20the%20hotel%2C%20she%20dramatically%20revealed%20the%20astonishing%20train%20attached%20to%20her%20Balenciaga%20bodycon%20design.%20The%20train%20measured%20a%20record-breaking%20500%20feet%20in%20length.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fkaty-perry-shocks-fans-with-500-foot-dress-train-featuring-lyrics-of-new-single-womans-world%2Farticleshow%2F111270898.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%227%20MPs%20Yet%20To%20Take%20Oath.%20What%20It%20Means%20For%20Opposition%20In%20Speaker%20Election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EToday's%20election%20for%20the%20post%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%2C%20already%20tilted%20in%20the%20government's%20favour%2C%20can%20push%20the%20Opposition%20further%20down%2C%20with%20five%20of%20its%20232%20MPs%20yet%20to%20take%20oath.%20The%20oath%20pending%2C%20they%20cannot%20vote%20in%20the%20election%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20includes%20stalwarts%20like%20Congress's%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress's%20actor-politician%20Shatrughan%20Sinha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20a%20few%20others%20--%20Deepak%20Adhikari%20and%20Nurul%20Islam%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20Afzhal%20Ansari%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20two%20Independents.%20It%20is%20not%20yet%20known%20why%20the%20oath%20of%20some%20of%20these%20leaders%20is%20pending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfzhal%20Ansari%20is%20the%20elder%20brother%20of%20criminal-turned-politician%20Mukhtar%20Ansari.%20Sentenced%20to%20four%20years%20in%20prison%2C%20his%20jail%20term%20was%20put%20on%20hold%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20in%20view%20of%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20will%20be%20heard%20when%20the%20court%20opens%20in%20July.%20If%20the%20court%20upholds%20his%20sentence%2C%20he%20will%20lose%20his%20membership%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVictory%20in%20Speaker%20election%20is%20based%20on%20the%20number%20of%20MPs%20present%20and%20voting%20-%20which%20means%20the%20absence%20of%20these%20seven%20MPs%20will%20bring%20down%20the%20total%20number%20and%20therefore%20the%20halfway%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Opposition%20won%20232%20seats%2C%20it%20will%20miss%20five%20MPs%20in%20its%20ranks%2C%20bringing%20it%20down%20to%20227%20-%20assuming%20the%20rest%20turn%20up%20and%20vote.%20The%20majority%20mark%20will%20stand%20at%20269.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%2C%20already%20with%20293%20MPs%2C%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20have%20the%20support%20of%20the%20four%20MPs%20of%20YS%20Jaganmohan%20Reddy's%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20which%2C%20like%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20had%20lent%20issue-based%20support%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20routed%20in%20the%20Odisha%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20BJD%20has%20said%20it%20will%20not%20provide%20any%20support%20to%20the%20BJP.%20But%20the%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20though%20trounced%20by%20BJP%20ally%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%2C%20is%20sticking%20to%20its%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20already%20has%20enough%20MPs%20in%20its%20corner%20to%20ensure%20a%20victory%20of%20Om%20Birla%20--%20who%20is%20contesting%20against%20Opposition%20candidate%20K%20Suresh%20for%20a%20second%20stint%20at%20the%20job%20--%20the%20question%20is%20one%20of%20optics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20also%20working%20to%20bring%20Harsimrat%20Kaur%20Badal%20of%20the%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20Nagina%20MP%20Chandrashekhar%20Azad%2C%20and%20Shillong%20MP%20Ricky%20Andrew%20Syngkon%20on%20board.%20With%20their%20support%2C%20the%20party%20aims%20to%20surpass%20the%20psychologically%20significant%20threshold%20of%20300%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%2C%20unlike%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20achieve%20majority%20on%20its%20own%20and%20is%20dependent%20on%20Mr%20Naidu's%20TDP%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20to%20keep%20its%20head%20above%20the%20halfway%20mark.%20A%20decisive%20victory%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20expected%20to%20boost%20morale%20in%20the%20party%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719364320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fsf9rik7g_rahul-gandhi-k-suresh_625x300_26_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-speaker-7-mps-yet-to-take-oath-what-it-means-for-opposition-in-speaker-election-5970857%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Today's%20election%20for%20the%20post%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%2C%20already%20tilted%20in%20the%20government's%20favour%2C%20can%20push%20the%20Opposition%20further%20down%2C%20with%20five%20of%20its%20232%20MPs%20yet%20to%20take%20oath.%20The%20oath%20pending%2C%20they%20cannot%20vote%20in%20the%20election%2C%20sources%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-speaker-7-mps-yet-to-take-oath-what-it-means-for-opposition-in-speaker-election-5970857%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-speaker-7-mps-yet-to-take-oath-what-it-means-for-opposition-in-speaker-election-5970857%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-speaker-7-mps-yet-to-take-oath-what-it-means-for-opposition-in-speaker-election-5970857%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata%20Sons%20to%20spend%20Rs%20750cr%20on%20building%20Ram%20temple%20museum%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719363537000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111271037%2Cimgsize-68