eative%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20need%20to%20have%20an%20honest%20public%20debate%20about%20the%20advantages%2C%20but%20also%20the%20pitfalls%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-new-dark-age-risks-regulations-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edangers%20of%20AI%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Astray%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that's%20not%20what%20she%20was%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0f7b209-8341-49e6-aab8-f512b4385233%5C%22%3E'Mediocre%20is%20all%20they%20want'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20tools%20could%20lower%20the%20barriers%20and%20allow%20anyone%20with%20an%20idea%20to%20create%2C%26quot%3B%20Murati%20wrote%20in%20her%20June%2022%20post%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20must%20be%20honest%20and%20acknowledge%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-could-automate-more-than-half-of-banking-jobs-citi-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20will%20automate%20certain%20tasks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Just%20like%20spreadsheets%20changed%20things%20for%20accountants%20and%20bookkeepers%2C%20AI%20tools%20can%20do%20things%20like%20writing%20online%20ads%20or%20making%20generic%20images%20and%20templates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20conversation%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-job-cuts-finance-wall-street-investment-banking-analysts-hiring-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-driven%20job%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20among%20creative%20professions%2C%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Brecognize%20the%20difference%20between%20temporary%20creative%20tasks%20and%20the%20kind%20that%20add%20lasting%20meaning%20and%20value%20to%20society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20AI%20tools%20taking%20on%20more%20repetitive%20or%20mechanistic%20aspects%20of%20the%20creative%20process%2C%20like%20generating%20SEO%20metada