Campbell%3B%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMy%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20I%20made%20our%20wedding%20possible%20by%20substituting%20high%20costs%20with%20budget%20alternatives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOpting%20for%20fake%20flowers%2C%20a%20friend%20as%20our%20officiant%2C%20and%20a%20honeymoon%20fund%20eased%20the%20financial%20strain.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fmy-financial-life%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20Financial%20Life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20helping%20people%20live%20and%20spend%20better.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20engaged%20in%20spring%202023%2C%20on%20my%2023rd%20birthday.%20Saying%20yes%20was%20easy%2C%20but%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20out%20how%20unaffordable%20even%20an%20%26quot%3Baffordable%26quot%3B%20wedding%20could%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20support%20from%20our%20respective%20families%2C%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20I%20had%20limited%20financial%20resources.%20Waiting%20a%20few%20years%20would've%20been%20the%20fiscally%20responsible%20choice%2C%20but%20the%20sheer%20excitement%20of%20getting%20married%20proved%20irresistible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20booked%20our%20date%20for%20just%20over%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20away%2C%20eager%20to%20tie%20the%20knot%20but%20with%20our%20tight%20budget%20hanging%20over%20our%20heads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20afford%20our%20wedding%2C%20we%20didn't%20DIY%20every%20decoration%20or%20skip%20out%20on%20necessary%20amenities.%20Instead%2C%20we%20stretched%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-budgeting-apps%5C%22%3Ebudget%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20substituting%20traditionally%20high%20expenses%20with%20more%20affordable%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20around%20120%20guests%2C%20we%20saved%20thousands.%20Here's%20how%20we%20focused%20our%20spending%20to%20afford%20our%202024%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22924157fa-c572-4084-9ef1-e41f3700d4ea%5C%22%3EI%20traded%20an%20expensive%20wedding%20cake%20for%20chocolate%20fondue%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tiered%20wedding%20cakes%20we%20looked%20at%20cost%20up%20to%20%241%2C000.%20Many%20cost%20even%20more%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20size%20and%20location.%20While%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20I%20both%20have%20intense%20sweet%20tooths%2C%20we%20didn't%20care%20much%20for%20the%20taste%20of%20expensive%20cake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20we%20opted%20for%20a%20more%20affordable%20dessert%20through%20our%20caterer.%20For%20a%20small%20upcharge%2C%20our%20caterer%20provided%20three%20chocolate-fondue%20fountains%20and%20an%20array%20of%20bite-size%20treats%20for%20dipping%2C%20saving%20us%20hundreds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20cake-cutting%20service%2C%20a%20cake-tasting%20session%2C%20or%20cake%20toppers.%20We%20used%20the%20extra%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20to%20book%20a%20pricier%20photographer%2C%20which%20we%20felt%20comfortable%20spending%20a%20little%20extra%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a6e0a43-b452-4890-b4a5-e4db7e3a25ae%5C%22%3EI%20saved%20thousands%20by%20buying%20fake%20flowers%20over%20real%20bouquets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D65b655930e344e320769831d1f5a4958393ceefd8b0b8412f819a09433f1f297%26postID%3D6671b8e3074e87bb00fdd3f0%26postSlug%3Dfocused-our-spending-afford-our-dream-wedding-2024-6%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.theknot.com%252Fcontent%252Faverage-cost-wedding-flowers%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Knot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20real%20flower%20bouquets%20cost%20an%20average%20of%20%242%2C800%20in%202023.%20Even%20on%20a%20budget%2C%20the%20florist%20we%20spoke%20to%20estimated%20that%20we%20would%20spend%20around%20%241%2C300%20to%20%241%2C800.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpending%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20on%20decorations%20with%20an%20expiration%20date%20felt%20wasteful%2C%20so%20I%20chose%20hand-dyed%20wooden%20flowers%20instead%2C%20which%20ended%20up%20costing%20around%20%24600.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20snagged%20an%20even%20bigger%20deal%20by%20waiting%20for%20a%20sale%20and%20dyeing%20them%20ourselves%20%E2%80%94%20in%20total%2C%20we%20saved%20around%20%24700%20to%20%241%2C200.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20was%20being%20able%20to%20contribute%20another%20personalized%20detail%20to%20our%20wedding%20day%20and%20create%20a%20cherished%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a4c2f818-50e0-4910-b4fd-64ee9358814a%5C%22%3EA%20mutual%20friend%20married%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDitching%20the%20traditional%20church%20ceremony%20allowed%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20me%20to%20create%20a%20space%20that%20reflected%20our%20unique%20wedding%20vision.%20However%2C%20this%20left%20us%20without%20an%20officiant%2C%20so%20we%20asked%20an%20ordained%20friend%20to%20step%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20matched%20our%20nontraditional%20vibe%20and%20saved%20us%20the%20cost%20of%20hiring%20an%20outside%20officiant.%20We%20used%20the%20money%20we%20saved%20to%20secure%20a%20reputable%20DJ%20who%20could%20easily%20provide%20music%20for%20both%20our%20ceremony%20and%20our%20reception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20married%20by%20a%20mutual%20friend%20added%20a%20layer%20of%20intimacy%2C%20which%20made%20that%20moment%20even%20more%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eada645c-5319-4506-9322-dde9e5273763%5C%22%3EI%20turned%20my%20wedding%20registry%20into%20a%20honeymoon%20fund%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBooking%20a%20honeymoon%20was%20the%20cherry%20on%20top%20of%20my%20financial-stress%20sundae.%20Upholding%20a%20wedding%20budget%20was%20hard%20enough%20without%20planning%20a%20trip%20on%20top%20of%20it.%20To%20lessen%20the%20financial%20burden%2C%20I%20turned%20my%20wedding%20registry%20into%20a%20honeymoon%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20won't%20lie%20%E2%80%94%20I%20did%20find%20the%20idea%20of%20shiny%2C%20new%20kitchen%20appliances%20and%20expensive%20home%20goods%20appealing.%20However%2C%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20I%20decided%20that%20creating%20one-of-a-kind%20memories%20together%20to%20start%20our%20married%20life%20was%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20opted%20for%20a%20honeymoon%20fund%20over%20a%20registry%20for%20both%20the%20shower%20and%20the%20wedding%20day.%20This%20allowed%20our%20friends%20and%20family%20to%20contribute%20whatever%20dollar%20amount%20they%20felt%20comfortable%20with%20as%20a%20gesture%20of%20love%20beyond%20material%20objects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20is%20that%20it%20worked!%20The%20combined%20contributions%20gave%20us%20more%20than%20enough%20to%20afford%20a%20luxury%20vacation%20without%20eating%20up%20what%20was%20left%20of%20our%20savings.%20Between%20having%20the%20cost%20of%20our%20honeymoon%20covered%20and%20all%20the%20other%20choices%20we%20made%2C%20we%20saved%20around%20%247%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESticking%20to%20a%20budget%20is%20wedding%20planning%20101%2C%20but%20strategic%20spending%20was%20how%20we%20made%20our%20dream%20wedding%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffocused-our-spending-afford-our-dream-wedding-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719349713000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671912670a95768a3115ff9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffocused-our-spending-afford-our-dream-wedding-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20I%20could%20afford%20our%20dream%20wedding%20in%202024%20by%20choosing%20budget-friendly%20alternatives%20and%20prioritizing%20strategic%20spendin