%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20a%20few%20tips%20to%20keep%20your%20mind%20calm%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStudy%20smarter%20and%20study%20harder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolve%20previous%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20(PYQ)%20papers%20and%20understand%20the%20topics%20UPSC%20has%20loved%20all%20these%20years.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20PYQs%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20mean%20just%20the%20questions%20but%20also%20the%20options.%20Observe%20why%20a%20question%20has%20been%20asked%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20seeing%20what%20has%20been%20asked%2C%20to%20understand%20the%20psyche%20of%20the%20question%20paper%20setter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20stop%2C%20but%20learn%20when%20to%20let%20go%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaruni%20quit%20her%20MBBS%20after%20two%20years%20due%20to%20a%20health%20problem.%20%E2%80%9CNever%20giving%20up%20is%20a%20good%20attitude%20that%20we%20all%20have%20been%20taught%20since%20we%20were%20kids.%20I%20made%20a%20similar%20mistake%20by%20not%20leaving%20my%20MBBS%20course%20early%20because%20I%20always%20felt%20that%20if%20I%20quit%2C%20it%20would%20be%20my%20failure.%20I%20realised%20later%20that%20there%20were%20equally%20good%20things%20in%20life%20waiting%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Taruni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20urges%20aspirants%20to%20make%20their%20own%20decisions%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20quitting%20or%20giving%20the%20exam%20another%20shot.%20%E2%80%9CListen%20to%20your%20conscience%20without%20paying%20any%20heed%20to%20the%20outside%20world%20and%20their%20set%20formats%20of%20success%20and%20failure%2C%20and%20you%20will%20get%20the%20correct%20answer.%20Move%20ahead%20with%20minimal%20regrets%20because%20zero%20regrets%20don%E2%80%99t%20exist%20for%20mere%20humans%20like%20us%2C%E2%80%9D