had%20been%20detected%20in%20groundwater%20in%20469%20districts%20across%2027%20states%20while%20arsenic%20has%20been%20detected%20in%20230%20districts%20across%2025%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entrepreneur%20successfully%20implemented%20a%20defluoridation%20system%20using%20electrolysis.%20His%20innovative%20method%20caused%20fluoride%20compounds%20to%20settle%2C%20providing%20villagers%20with%20clean%2C%20fluoride-free%20water.%20This%20project%20in%202009%20kicked%20off%20his%20mission%20to%20provide%20clean%20drinking%20water%20to%20every%20household%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERite%20Water%20Solutions%20has%20different%20solutions%20available%20vis-a-vis%20water%20purification%20including%20decentralised%20water%20purification%20systems%2C%20solar-powered%20water%20treatment%20units%2C%20and%20mobile%20water%20ATMs.%20Some%20of%20these%20are%20developed%20in-house%20while%20a%20few%20have%20been%20developed%20through%20tie-ups%20with%20research%20labs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Frite4-1718797991.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rite%20Water%20provides%20clean%20drinking%20water%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Frite4-1718797991.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Frite4-1718797991-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Frite4-1718797991-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Frite4-1718797991-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Frite4-1718797991-1536x1023.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-medi