ar%20dryers%20came%20in.%20As%20Latika%E2%80%99s%20son%20Ninad%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20any%20climatic%20circumstances%2C%20the%20temperature%20of%20these%20plates%20is%20maintained%20at%2055%20to%2060%20degrees%2C%20which%20helps%20in%20conserving%20the%20nutrients.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%20that%20the%20plates%20are%20covered%20by%20UV%20protection%20high-grade%20polycarbonate%20sheets%2C%20which%20also%20protect%20the%20contents%20from%20dust%20and%20external%20particles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20profitability%20gained%20by%20venturing%20into%20solar%20drying%20is%20exponential%2C%20as%20Latika%20shares.%20Not%20only%20does%20it%20reduce%20the%20processing%20time%20of%20the%20fruit%20to%20one%20day%20compared%20to%20three%20to%20four%20days%2C%20she%20says%2C%20but%20it%20also%20increases%20the%20shelf-life%20to%20nine%20months%20from%20the%20previous%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReach%20out%20to%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fauragreenwellness.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Solar%20power%20for%20running%20homestays%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20beautiful%20homestay%20in%20Manali%20is%20powered%20entirely%20by%20solar%20and%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20sustainability%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.t