his%20experience%20made%20me%20realise%20the%20power%20of%20collective%20action.%20Back%20in%202013%2C%20I%20had%20already%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20platform%20for%20people%20like%20me%20who%20were%20passionate%20about%20social%20change.%20Although%20I%20was%20working%20with%20the%20Art%20of%20Living%20Foundation%2C%20I%20had%20limited%20connections%20with%20other%20social%20impact%20organisations%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20in%20my%20family%20had%20been%20involved%20in%20social%20work%2C%20so%20this%20was%20my%20first%20introduction%20to%20such%20projects%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202019%20floods%20also%2C%20Neenu%20actively%20participated%20in%20the%20rehabilitation%20of%20people%20affected%20by%20the%20disaster%2C%20particularly%20focusing%20on%20tribal%20settlements%20in%20Attapadi%2C%20Nilambur%2C%20and%20Wayanad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20motivation%20that%20came%20from%20helping%20people%20in%20need%20kept%20me%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20when%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20Neenu%20realised%20that%20it%20was%20important%20for%20her%20to%20work%20on%20her%20idea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20heart%2C%20it%20was%20more%20like%20a%20project%20for%20me%20and%20I%20had%20never%20thought%20of%20becoming%20a%20social%20entrepreneur.%20After%20it%20was%20incubated%20at%20NSRCEL%20(Nadathur%20S.%20Raghavan%20Centre%20for%20Entrepreneurial%20Learning)%2C%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20I%20realised%20this%20initiative%20had%20much%20more%20potential%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFoundation%20for%20Social%20Town%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20non-profit%20organisation%20was%20started%20with%20500%20people%20and%20has%20engaged%20more%20than%206%2C000%20people%20in%20social%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20initially%20use